---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import StatsBar from '../../components/StatsBar.astro';
---

<Base title="Cybersécurité — pixelium.win" description="Parcours cybersécurité offensive de Stéphane — Hack The Box (rang Hacker, #967), TryHackMe, Root-Me. Présenté par Claude.">
  <main>
    <section class="hero-mini">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="terminal-prompt">$ ./recon.sh --target self</p>
        <h1>Cybersécurité<span class="dot">.</span></h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Apprendre à attaquer pour mieux défendre. Stéphane ne se contente pas de protéger son infrastructure — il comprend les techniques de ceux qui voudraient la compromettre.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- La démarche -->
    <section class="layer">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="layer-header">
          <span class="layer-number">01</span>
          <h2>La démarche</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="layer-content">
          <p>Chaque technique offensive apprise renforce directement une couche défensive du homelab. Ce n'est pas du hobbyisme — c'est une <strong>boucle de feedback entre l'attaque et la défense.</strong></p>
          <div class="feedback-loop">
            <div class="loop-item">
              <span class="loop-arrow">&#8594;</span>
              <div>
                <span class="loop-offense">Password spraying sur HTB</span>
                <span class="loop-result">&#8594; Politiques de complexité renforcées sur Authentik</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="loop-item">
              <span class="loop-arrow">&#8594;</span>
              <div>
                <span class="loop-offense">MSSQL impersonation</span>
                <span class="loop-result">&#8594; Audit des permissions de service sur le homelab</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="loop-item">
              <span class="loop-arrow">&#8594;</span>
              <div>
                <span class="loop-offense">Kerberoasting / AD enum</span>
                <span class="loop-result">&#8594; Monitoring SPN et tickets Kerberos dans Wazuh</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="loop-item">
              <span class="loop-arrow">&#8594;</span>
              <div>
                <span class="loop-offense">Hash cracking PBKDF2</span>
                <span class="loop-result">&#8594; Vérification des algorithmes de hashing sur chaque service</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Profils plateformes -->
    <section class="layer">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="layer-header">
          <span class="layer-number">02</span>
          <h2>Profils</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="layer-content">
          <p>Apprentissage actif sur trois plateformes de cybersécurité — les références mondiales de l'entraînement offensif. Ce ne sont pas des jeux — ce sont des environnements réalistes utilisés par les professionnels, les pentesters et les équipes de sécurité du monde entier pour affûter leurs compétences face à des scénarios d'attaque réels.</p>
          <div class="platforms-grid">

            <!-- HTB -->
            <a href="https://app.hackthebox.com/users/1161145" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="platform-card htb-card">
              <div class="platform-header">
                <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;">
                  <img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/hackthebox/9FEF00" alt="" class="platform-logo" loading="lazy" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
                  <span class="platform-name">Hack The Box</span>
                </div>
                <span class="platform-rank">Hacker</span>
              </div>
              <div class="platform-stats">
                <div class="platform-stat">
                  <span class="stat-number">23</span>
                  <span class="stat-label">Machines</span>
                </div>
                <div class="platform-stat">
                  <span class="stat-number">13</span>
                  <span class="stat-label">Challenges</span>
                </div>
                <div class="platform-stat">
                  <span class="stat-number">61</span>
                  <span class="stat-label">Flags</span>
                </div>
                <div class="platform-stat">
                  <span class="stat-number">#967</span>
                  <span class="stat-label">Global</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="platform-desc">La plateforme mondiale de référence en sécurité offensive. Machines vulnérables réalistes — du scan initial au root complet. Active Directory Windows, escalade de privilèges Linux, exploitation web, recherche de CVE. Utilisée par les professionnels et les red teams du monde entier. Le terrain d'entraînement principal de Stéphane.</p>
              <span class="platform-cta">Voir le profil &#8594;</span>
            </a>

            <!-- THM -->
            <a href="https://tryhackme.com/p/ferr0" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="platform-card thm-card">
              <div class="platform-header">
                <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;">
                  <img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/tryhackme/ef3b36" alt="" class="platform-logo" loading="lazy" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
                  <span class="platform-name">TryHackMe</span>
                </div>
                <span class="platform-rank thm-rank">Hacker</span>
              </div>
              <div class="platform-stats">
                <div class="platform-stat">
                  <span class="stat-number">35</span>
                  <span class="stat-label">Rooms</span>
                </div>
                <div class="platform-stat">
                  <span class="stat-number">7</span>
                  <span class="stat-label">Badges</span>
                </div>
                <div class="platform-stat">
                  <span class="stat-number">Top 15%</span>
                  <span class="stat-label">Rang</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="platform-desc">L'une des plateformes d'apprentissage cybersécurité les plus populaires au monde. Parcours guidés et rooms thématiques — apprentissage structuré du pentest aux opérations SOC. Accessible aux débutants avec une difficulté progressive. Utilisée par les universités et la préparation aux certifications.</p>
              <span class="platform-cta">Voir le profil &#8594;</span>
            </a>

            <!-- Root-Me -->
            <a href="https://www.root-me.org/Ferr0" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="platform-card rootme-card">
              <div class="platform-header">
                <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;">
                  <img src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/rootme/ffc107" alt="" class="platform-logo" loading="lazy" aria-hidden="true" onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
                  <span class="platform-name">Root-Me</span>
                </div>
                <span class="platform-rank rootme-rank">765 pts</span>
              </div>
              <div class="platform-stats">
                <div class="platform-stat">
                  <span class="stat-number">63</span>
                  <span class="stat-label">Challenges</span>
                </div>
                <div class="platform-stat">
                  <span class="stat-number">10%</span>
                  <span class="stat-label">Validations</span>
                </div>
                <div class="platform-stat">
                  <span class="stat-number">3</span>
                  <span class="stat-label">Badges</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="platform-desc">La plateforme CTF de référence en Europe, née en France. Challenges techniques ciblés — exploitation web, cryptographie, forensics, analyse réseau. Reconnue pour sa profondeur et son contenu communautaire. Une référence dans la cybersécurité francophone.</p>
              <span class="platform-cta">Voir le profil &#8594;</span>
            </a>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Techniques -->
    <section class="layer">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="layer-header">
          <span class="layer-number">03</span>
          <h2>Techniques pratiquées</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="layer-content">
          <p>Compétences acquises et validées sur des environnements réels — pas de la théorie, des <strong>flags capturés.</strong></p>
          <div class="techniques-grid">
            <div class="technique-group">
              <h4>Active Directory</h4>
              <div class="technique-tags">
                <span>Kerberoasting</span>
                <span>AS-REP Roasting</span>
                <span>ACL abuse</span>
                <span>MSSQL impersonation</span>
                <span>Password spraying</span>
                <span>BloodHound enum</span>
                <span>WinRM lateral movement</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="technique-group">
              <h4>Exploitation web</h4>
              <div class="technique-tags">
                <span>SQLi</span>
                <span>SSTI</span>
                <span>LFI / RFI</span>
                <span>Command injection</span>
                <span>OAuth redirect abuse</span>
                <span>Cookie manipulation</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="technique-group">
              <h4>Cryptographie & cracking</h4>
              <div class="technique-tags">
                <span>Hashcat (PBKDF2, bcrypt)</span>
                <span>John the Ripper</span>
                <span>Hash identification</span>
                <span>Salt extraction</span>
                <span>GPU cracking (RTX 3090)</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="technique-group">
              <h4>Énumération & reconnaissance</h4>
              <div class="technique-tags">
                <span>Nmap</span>
                <span>Gobuster / ffuf</span>
                <span>SMB enum</span>
                <span>SNMP walk</span>
                <span>DNS zone transfer</span>
                <span>Service fingerprinting</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="technique-group">
              <h4>Escalade de privilèges</h4>
              <div class="technique-tags">
                <span>SUID / capabilities</span>
                <span>Sudo misconfiguration</span>
                <span>Cron abuse</span>
                <span>Kernel exploits</span>
                <span>Service permissions</span>
                <span>Token impersonation</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="technique-group">
              <h4>Outils</h4>
              <div class="technique-tags">
                <span>Impacket</span>
                <span>Evil-WinRM</span>
                <span>Netexec</span>
                <span>Metasploit</span>
                <span>Burp Suite</span>
                <span>Chisel / ligolo</span>
                <span>LinPEAS / WinPEAS</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Environnement -->
    <section class="layer">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="layer-header">
          <span class="layer-number">04</span>
          <h2>L'environnement</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="layer-content">
          <p>Même le lab offensif est bien architecturé — isolation, performances, et zéro compromis sur la sécurité de la workstation.</p>
          <div class="specs">
            <div class="spec">
              <span class="spec-label">OS</span>
              <span class="spec-value">Kali Linux en distrobox sur Bluefin — conteneur isolé, pas de VM lourde ni dual boot</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec">
              <span class="spec-label">Setup choisi</span>
              <span class="spec-value">On a longtemps bataillé pour faire tourner Exegol — le setup que l'on voulait. L'archi atomic de Bluefin (composefs read-only, Podman rootless) l'a rendu impossible. Kali distrobox est la solution pragmatique. Contrainte réelle, compromis assumé.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec">
              <span class="spec-label">GPU cracking</span>
              <span class="spec-value">RTX 3090 24 Go — hashcat mode 10900 (PBKDF2) à pleine vitesse, <code>nvidia-smi -pl 250</code> pour le thermique</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec">
              <span class="spec-label">Réseau</span>
              <span class="spec-value">VPN HTB isolé dans le conteneur Kali — trafic offensif séparé du LAN homelab</span>
            </div>
            <div class="spec">
              <span class="spec-label">Binôme</span>
              <span class="spec-value">Claude en mode tuteur — guidance sans spoiler, questions socratiques, debriefs post-box</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Stats -->
    <StatsBar stats={[
      { number: '22', label: 'machines HTB' },
      { number: '59', label: 'flags capturés' },
      { number: '#967', label: 'rang mondial HTB' },
      { number: '3', label: 'plateformes actives' },
    ]} />

    <!-- Lien défense -->
    <section class="crosslink reveal">
      <div class="container">
        <a href="/securite" class="crosslink-block">
          <div>
            <h3>&#9670; Stack défensive</h3>
            <p>PKI interne, SSO Authentik, CrowdSec IPS, Wazuh SIEM, Headscale VPN — les 5 couches défensives du homelab, construites avec les leçons de l'offensive.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="crosslink-arrow">&#8594;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>

<style>
  /* Hero mini */
  .hero-mini {
    padding: 4rem 0 3rem;
  }

  .terminal-prompt {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .dot {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .subtitle {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    max-width: 42rem;
  }

  /* Layers */
  .layer {
    padding: 3rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .layer-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .layer-number {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .layer-header h2 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .platform-logo {
    width: 1.4rem;
    height: 1.4rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .layer-content > p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .layer-content > p strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  /* Feedback loop */
  .feedback-loop {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .loop-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 6px;
  }

  .loop-arrow {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .loop-item > div {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .loop-offense {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #f87171;
    background: rgba(248, 113, 113, 0.1);
    padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(248, 113, 113, 0.2);
  }

  .loop-result {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  /* Platform cards */
  .platforms-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(18rem, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .platform-card {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    transition: border-color 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
  }

  a.platform-card {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
  }

  a.platform-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1);
    color: inherit;
  }

  .htb-card {
    border-top: 3px solid #9fef00;
  }

  .thm-card {
    border-top: 3px solid #ef3b36;
  }

  .rootme-card {
    border-top: 3px solid #ffc107;
  }

  .platform-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .platform-name {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .platform-rank {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: rgba(159, 239, 0, 0.1);
    color: #9fef00;
    border: 1px solid rgba(159, 239, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .platform-rank.thm-rank {
    background: rgba(239, 59, 54, 0.1);
    color: #ef3b36;
    border-color: rgba(239, 59, 54, 0.3);
  }

  .platform-rank.rootme-rank {
    background: rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.1);
    color: #ffc107;
    border-color: rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.3);
  }

  .platform-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .platform-stat {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-number {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .platform-desc {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .platform-cta {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  /* Techniques grid */
  .techniques-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(16rem, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .technique-group {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
  }

  .technique-group h4 {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .technique-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .technique-tags span {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  /* Specs */
  .specs {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .spec {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 0.6rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    align-items: baseline;
  }

  .spec:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .spec-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    min-width: 7rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .spec-value {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  /* Crosslink */
  .crosslink {
    padding: 2rem 0 3rem;
  }

  .crosslink-block {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 2rem;
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.2);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.05), rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.02));
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: border-color 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
  }

  .crosslink-block:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1);
    color: inherit;
  }

  .crosslink-block h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .crosslink-block p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-width: 42rem;
  }

  .crosslink-arrow {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .spec {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.25rem;
    }
    .spec-label {
      min-width: unset;
    }
    .loop-item > div {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .platform-stats {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
    .crosslink-block {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
